  "keyFeatures": [
    "Hourly auto-updating KML files via GitHub Actions",
    "Direct raw URL access for GIS software import",
    "Interactive web interface with map preview",
    "SafeAirspace aviation risk warnings with country polygons and NOTAMs",
    "Real-time Israel rocket alert zones updated every 5 minutes",
    "ICE protest event mapping from Mobilize.us",
    "Cloudflare Pages hosting with zero cost"
